1. [Specific yes/no question derived from criterion]
2. [Specific yes/no question derived from criterion]
3. [Specific yes/no question derived from criterion]

## Decision Rule
- PASS if: [Clear condition based on criterion]
- FAIL if: [Clear condition based on criterion]

## Content to Evaluate
Input: {input}
Output: {output}

Does the output pass this criterion? Evaluate based on the questions above.
```

